  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>Thank you for playing <strong>Clone Legion 3D</strong>. This privacy policy explains how we handle your data. Spoiler: we currently don’t collect any personal information, but we might in the future if features like ads or analytics are added.</p>

  <h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
  <p>As of now, <strong>Clone Legion 3D</strong> does <strong>not collect any personal information</strong>. We do not access your name, email, location, or any other personal data.</p>
  <p>In future updates, we may introduce:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Advertising (e.g. AdMob or similar platforms)</li>
    <li>Analytics (e.g. Google Firebase)</li>
    <li>In-app purchases</li>
  </ul>
  <p>If any data collection features are added, this policy will be updated accordingly and transparently.</p>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not share any information with third parties, because we don’t collect any.</p>

  <h2>4. User Rights</h2>
  <p>If we collect data in the future, users will have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Know what data is collected</li>
    <li>Access, modify, or delete their data</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Policy Changes</h2>
  <p>Any changes to this policy will be posted at this URL. We will notify you in the app if major updates are made.</p>

  <h2>6. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about this policy, feel free to contact us:</p>
  <p><strong>Email:</strong> CloneLegion3D@outlook.com</p>
